name: merongmix+
description:
I made this mixture model with dosmix, grapemix, orangemix2, pastelmix and anything4.5.

I mostly use this model with huge negative prompts, almost 300 tokens. However, you can use simple negative prompts, "(low quality, worst quality:1.4), (realistic:1)".

Without huge negative prompts, the model usually makes almost naked girls.

If you want other things, you should make them with well-made prompts.

I strongly recommend using highres.fix with about 1.5x. (I usually make 512*1152->768*1728 and 1024*704->1536*1056)

I haven't tested NSFW images, but I think the model will make NSFW well because I mixed the grapemix and orangemix2-hard.

I usually use anything 4.0 VAE and didn't test other VAEs. If you try other VAEs, please share your experience.

I recommend anything 4.0 VAE and kl-f8-anime2 VAE.

Thanks
